        "content": "<p>We're writing to inform you about updates to our Privacy Policy, effective <strong>January 1, 2025</strong>. These changes reflect our ongoing commitment to transparency and protecting your data.</p><p style='margin-top: 24px;'>Here's what's changing:</p>",
